## Known issues fixed

### gnomAD variant normalisation (fixed -- March 2026)
Early versions returned "not in gnomAD" for some variants that
genuinely exist in the database. Root cause: Ensembl and gnomAD
use different allele orientations for some variants. Fix: agent
now tries both REF/ALT and ALT/REF orientations automatically.
